title: Internet Speed Meter v1.4.8
description:
******

Internet Speed Meter Apk displays your Internet speed in stats bar and shows the amount of data used in notification panel. This helps you to monitor network connection profile anytime while using your device.

Key Features:

Real time speed update in status bar and notification
Daily traffic usage in notification
Separate stats for mobile network and WiFi network
Monitors your traffic data for the last 30 days
Battery efficient
Smarter notifications
Themes support
Blue status bar icon
Upload and download speed
